<inglise>"(1) A state official shall not belong to the permanent directing body or permanent control or audit body of a commercial association, except as a representative of the state to the directing or supervisory body of an enterprise with holding of the state or a person in public law." </inglise>
<eesti>; </eesti>
<inglise>; </inglise>
<eesti>7) paragrahv 75 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>7) subsection 75 is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 75. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 75. </inglise>
<eesti>Majanduslike huvide deklareerimise kohustus </eesti>
<inglise>Duty to declare economic interest </inglise>
