<eesti>8) paragrahvi 76 tekst muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>8) the text of &sect; 76 is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(1) Teenistujal on keelatud: </eesti>
<inglise>"(1) A public servant is prohibited from: </inglise>
<eesti>1) omandada tehingu tegemiseks tema k&auml;tte usaldatud selle isiku vara, kellega ta on t&ouml;&ouml;- v&otilde;i teenistussuhtes; </eesti>
<inglise>1) acquiring assets which are entrusted to him or her for concluding a transaction and belong to a person with whom he or she is in employment or service relationship and; </inglise>
<eesti>2) teha riigiasutust tehingus esindama &otilde;igustatud isikuna asjaomase ametiasutuse kaudu tehinguid riigiga v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse asutust tehingus esindama &otilde;igustatud isikuna asjaomase ametiasutuse kaudu tehinguid kohaliku omavalitsus&uuml;ksusega; </eesti>
<inglise>2) concluding, as a person entitled to represent a state agency in transactions, transactions with the state through the administrative agency concerned, or concluding, as a person entitled to represent a local government agency in transactions, transactions with a local government through the administrative agency concerned; </inglise>
<eesti>3) teha riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse esindajana varalisi tehinguid korruptsioonivastase seaduse &sect; 19 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud juriidiliste isikutega; </eesti>
<inglise>3) concluding, as a representative of the state or a local government, property transactions with legal persons specified in subsection 19 (2) of the Anti-corruption Act; </inglise>
<eesti>4) teha riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse esindajana varalisi tehinguid mittetulundus&uuml;hingu v&otilde;i erakonnaga, mille liige ta on; </eesti>
<inglise>4) concluding, as a representative of the state or a local government, property transactions with a non-profit association or political party of which he or she is a member; </inglise>
<eesti>5) teha riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse esindajana varalisi tehinguid selle t&ouml;&ouml;andja, &auml;ri&uuml;hingu, mittetulundus&uuml;hingu v&otilde;i erakonnaga, kelle tegevust ta kontrollib; </eesti>
<inglise>5) concluding, as a representative of the state or a local government, property transactions with an employer, company, non-profit association or political party, over the activities of which he or she exercises supervision; </inglise>
<eesti>6) teha riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse esindajana varalisi tehinguid oma l&auml;hisugulaste, -h&otilde;imlaste v&otilde;i iseendaga. </eesti>
<inglise>6) concluding, as a representative of the state or a local government, property transactions with his or her close relatives, close relatives by marriage or himself or herself. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud keeldu rikkudes tehtud tehing on t&uuml;hine." </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Transactions concluded in violation of the prohibitions provided for in subsection (1) of this section are void." </inglise>
<eesti>; </eesti>
