<eesti>Kriminaalkoodeksis (RT 1992, 20, 288; RT I 1997, 21/22, 353; 28, 423; 30, 472; 34, 535; 51, 824; 52, 833 ja 834; 81, 1361; 86, 1461; 87, 1466-1468; 1998, 2, 42; 4, 62; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 412; 36/37, 552 ja 553; 51, 756 ja 759; 59, 941; 98/99, 1576; 107, 1766; 108/109, 1783; 1999, 4, 53) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused ja t&auml;iendused: </eesti>
<inglise>The Criminal Code (RT 1992, 20, 288; RT I 1997, 21/22, 353; 28, 423; 30, 472; 34, 535; 51, 824; 52, 833 and 834; 81, 1361; 86, 1461; 87, 1466-1468; 1998, 2, 42; 4, 62; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 412; 36/37, 552 and 553; 51, 756 and 759; 59, 941; 98/99, 1576; 107, 1766; 108/109, 1783; 1999, 4, 53) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 27 l&otilde;iget 1 t&auml;iendatakse p&auml;rast s&otilde;nu "teataval tegevusalal tegutsemise" s&otilde;nadega "v&otilde;i avalikus teenistuses olemise" ja asendatakse s&otilde;na "kolme" s&otilde;naga "viie"; </eesti>
<inglise>1) subsection 27 (1) is amended by adding the words "or employment in the public service" after the words "operation in the particular area of activity", and the word "three" is substituted by the word "five"; </inglise>
<eesti>2) koodeksit t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 162 (1) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) section 1621 is added to the Code worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 162 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 162 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>Korruptsioonivastase seadusega kehtestatud t&ouml;&ouml;koha-, tegevus- v&otilde;i toimingupiirangute rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of restrictions on employment and activities, or procedural restrictions established by Anti-corruption Act </inglise>
<eesti>Korruptsioonivastase seadusega kehtestatud t&ouml;&ouml;koha-, tegevus- v&otilde;i toimingupiirangute rikkumise eest, kui: 1) sellega p&otilde;hjustati oluline varaline kahju v&otilde;i muu raske tagaj&auml;rg isiku, riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse seadusega kaitstud &otilde;igustele v&otilde;i huvidele v&otilde;i kui </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of restrictions on employment and activities, or procedural restrictions established by the Anti-corruption Act is punishable by up to two years' imprisonment together with deprivation the right of employment in the particular office or operation in a particular area of activity or employment in the public service if: </inglise>
<eesti>2) s&uuml;&uuml;dlasele oli samasuguse tegevuse eest kohaldatud halduskaristust, - karistatakse vabadusekaotusega kuni kahe aastani &uuml;hes teataval ametikohal t&ouml;&ouml;tamise v&otilde;i teataval tegevusalal tegutsemise v&otilde;i avalikus teenistuses olemise &otilde;iguse &auml;rav&otilde;tmisega." </eesti>
<inglise>1) a significant proprietary damage or other serious consequence to the rights or interests of a person, the state or a local government protected by law has been caused thereby, or if 2) an administrative punishment has been imposed on the offender for the same act." </inglise>
<eesti>; </eesti>
<inglise>; </inglise>
<eesti>3) koodeksit t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 162 (2) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>3) section 1622 is added to the Code worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 162 (2). </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 162 (2). </inglise>
<eesti>Korruptsiooniohtlikust suhtest teatamata j&auml;tmine </eesti>
<inglise>Failure to give notification of relationship involving risk of corruption </inglise>
<eesti>Korruptsiooniohtlikust suhtest teatamata j&auml;tmise eest, kui 1) sellega p&otilde;hjustati oluline varaline kahju v&otilde;i muu raske tagaj&auml;rg isiku, riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse seadusega kaitstud &otilde;igustele v&otilde;i huvidele v&otilde;i kui </eesti>
<inglise>Failure to give notification of a relationship involving the risk of corruption is punishable by a fine or up to one year imprisonment together with deprivation of the right of employment in the particular office or operation in the particular area of activity or employment in the public service if: </inglise>
<eesti>2) s&uuml;&uuml;dlasele oli samasuguse tegevuse eest kohaldatud halduskaristust, - karistatakse rahatrahvi v&otilde;i vabadusekaotusega kuni &uuml;he aastani &uuml;hes teataval ametikohal t&ouml;&ouml;tamise v&otilde;i teataval tegevusalal tegutsemise v&otilde;i avalikus teenistuses olemise &otilde;iguse &auml;rav&otilde;tmisega." </eesti>
<inglise>1) a significant proprietary damage or other serious consequence to the rights or interests of a person, the state or a local government protected by law has been caused thereby, or if 2) administrative penalty has been imposed to the person at fault for the same act." </inglise>
<eesti>; </eesti>
<inglise>; </inglise>
<eesti>4) koodeksit t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 162 (3) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
