<eesti>Avalikustamisele kuuluva majanduslike huvide deklaratsiooni esitamata j&auml;tmine v&otilde;i selles valeandmete esitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Failure to submit declaration of economic interests subject to disclosure, or presentation of false information therein </inglise>
<eesti>(1) N&otilde;uetekohase avalikustamisele kuuluva majanduslike huvide deklaratsiooni t&auml;htajaks esitamata j&auml;tmise v&otilde;i selles mittet&auml;ielike v&otilde;i valeandmete esitamise eest - karistatakse rahatrahvi v&otilde;i arestiga. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Failure to submit a declaration of economic interests subject to disclosure in accordance with the requirements during the term, or presentation of incomplete or false information therein shall be punished by a fine or detention. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sama teo eest, kui sellega p&otilde;hjustati oluline varaline kahju v&otilde;i muu raske tagaj&auml;rg isiku, riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse seadusega kaitstud &otilde;igustele v&otilde;i huvidele, - karistatakse rahatrahvi v&otilde;i vabadusekaotusega kuni &uuml;he aastani &uuml;hes vastaval ametikohal t&ouml;&ouml;tamise v&otilde;i teataval tegevusalal tegutsemise v&otilde;i avalikus teenistuses olemise &otilde;iguse &auml;rav&otilde;tmisega." </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The same act shall be punished by a fine or imprisonment for up to one year together with taking away the right of employment in the particular office or operation in the particular area of activity or employment in the public service if a significant proprietary damage or other serious consequence to the rights or interests of a person, the state or a local government protected by law has been caused thereby." </inglise>
