<inglise>Failure to submit a declaration of economic interests not subject to disclosure in accordance with the requirements during the term or presentation of incomplete or false information therein shall be punished by a fine or imprisonment for up to one year together with taking away the right of employment in the particular office or operation in the particular area of activity or employment in the public service if </inglise>
